# Multi-Agent Orchestrator

## Purpose
Implements a real execution engine for multi-agent workflows.

## Key Features
- Spawns separate LLM calls for each specialist agent.
- Executes tasks in sequence or parallel based on dependencies.
- Integrates results from multiple agents.
- Handles errors and retries.

## Usage
- Run tasks with specific models.
- Orchestrate complex workflows.
- Integrate with other agents for task execution.
